{"id":2279,"category_slug":"medical-english-oet","category_name":"Medical English (OET)","position":14,"title":"Test 02 - Part B - Extract 2","subtitle":"MRI Scan Preparation","level":"B1","parts":11,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2.2279/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/0-test-02-part-b-extract-2.mp3","transcript":"Come in, come in... Mrs Brown, isn't it?\nMy name's Ted and I'm going to be doing your MRI scan today.\nNow, can you get up on the table for me?\nYou know, I'm really claustrophobic.\nWell, this is a new piece of equipment.\nThe diameter's much larger, so it should make it a little more comfortable for you.\nYou'll also have this call bell, so if you need me at any point during the test, you squeeze that, okay?\nOkay.\nNow your scan's only going to take about 15 minutes, are you okay with that?\nI am.\nOkay, let's get started then.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:52:42","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Come in, come in... Mrs Brown, isn't it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/1.mp3","time_start":0.45,"time_end":3.05},{"position":2,"content":"My name's Ted and I'm going to be doing your MRI scan today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/2.mp3","time_start":3.05,"time_end":6.35},{"position":3,"content":"Now, can you get up on the table for me?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/3.mp3","time_start":6.35,"time_end":9.14},{"position":4,"content":"You know, I'm really claustrophobic.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/4.mp3","time_start":9.45,"time_end":12.21},{"position":5,"content":"Well, this is a new piece of equipment.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/5.mp3","time_start":12.29,"time_end":14.47},{"position":6,"content":"The diameter's much larger, so it should make it a little more comfortable for you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/6.mp3","time_start":14.47,"time_end":18.19},{"position":7,"content":"You'll also have this call bell, so if you need me at any point during the test, you squeeze that, okay?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/7.mp3","time_start":18.69,"time_end":24.21},{"position":8,"content":"Okay.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/8.mp3","time_start":24.21,"time_end":24.99},{"position":9,"content":"Now your scan's only going to take about 15 minutes, are you okay with that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/9.mp3","time_start":24.99,"time_end":28.48},{"position":10,"content":"I am.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/10.mp3","time_start":28.48,"time_end":30.33},{"position":11,"content":"Okay, let's get started then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/medical-english-oet/test-02-part-b-extract-2-2025-08-29-21-08-34/11.mp3","time_start":30.33,"time_end":32.15}]}